description: Deletes tags from a resource. You must provide the ARN of the resource from which you want to delete the tag or tags.

parameters.name: ResourceName
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) from which you want to remove the tag or tags. For example, arn:aws:redshift:us-east-2:123456789:cluster:t1.

parameters.name: TagKeys
parameters.description: The tag key that you want to delete. (string) ---
